## 6. Tạo Docker Compose và khởi động 2 container

### 6.1 Tạo file docker-compose.yml

```bash
sudo vim /opt/camunda-docker/docker-compose.yml
```

```yaml
services:
  camunda1:
    image: camunda-oracle:7.24.0
    container_name: camunda1
    restart: unless-stopped
    ports:
      - "8081:8080"
    environment:
      - SKIP_DB_CONFIG=true
      - WAIT_FOR=192.168.1.127:1521
      - WAIT_FOR_TIMEOUT=60
      - JAVA_OPTS=-Xms1g -Xmx2g -XX:+UseG1GC -XX:MaxGCPauseMillis=200 -Djava.awt.headless=true
    volumes:
      - ./config/server.xml:/camunda/conf/server.xml:ro
    deploy:
      resources:
        limits:
          memory: 3g
          cpus: "2.0"
    healthcheck:
      test: ["CMD-SHELL", "curl -sf http://localhost:8080/camunda/api/engine/engine || exit 1"]
      interval: 30s
      timeout: 10s
      retries: 5
      start_period: 60s
    logging:
      driver: "json-file"
      options:
        max-size: "50m"
        max-file: "5"

  camunda2:
    image: camunda-oracle:7.24.0
    container_name: camunda2
    restart: unless-stopped
    ports:
      - "8082:8080"
    environment:
      - SKIP_DB_CONFIG=true
      - WAIT_FOR=192.168.1.127:1521
      - WAIT_FOR_TIMEOUT=60
      - JAVA_OPTS=-Xms1g -Xmx2g -XX:+UseG1GC -XX:MaxGCPauseMillis=200 -Djava.awt.headless=true
    volumes:
      - ./config/server.xml:/camunda/conf/server.xml:ro
    deploy:
      resources:
        limits:
          memory: 3g
          cpus: "2.0"
    healthcheck:
      test: ["CMD-SHELL", "curl -sf http://localhost:8080/camunda/api/engine/engine || exit 1"]
      interval: 30s
      timeout: 10s
      retries: 5
      start_period: 60s
    logging:
      driver: "json-file"
      options:
        max-size: "50m"
        max-file: "5"
```

### Giải thích các tham số quan trọng

```text
SKIP_DB_CONFIG=true     → Không để entrypoint script ghi đè cấu hình DB (ta dùng server.xml custom)
WAIT_FOR=...            → Container đợi Oracle DB sẵn sàng trước khi start Tomcat
JAVA_OPTS               → JVM tuning: heap 1-2GB, G1GC, max pause 200ms
memory: 3g              → Container limit = Xmx (2g) × 1.5 → headroom cho JVM non-heap
restart: unless-stopped → Tự restart sau reboot (khi Docker service đã enable)
healthcheck             → Docker tự kiểm tra Camunda có respond không, mỗi 30 giây
```

> **Lưu ý RAM:** Server B cần tối thiểu **8GB RAM** (3g × 2 container + OS overhead).
> Nếu server chỉ có 4GB RAM, giảm xuống:
> ```yaml
> JAVA_OPTS: -Xms512m -Xmx1g ...
> limits:
>   memory: 1536m
> ```

