## 18. Giám sát cơ bản

### Health check script (đặt trên Server A)

```bash
sudo vim /opt/camunda-healthcheck.sh
```

```bash
#!/bin/bash
# Kiểm tra cả 2 node Camunda qua Nginx

NGINX_URL="http://localhost:7777/engine-rest/engine"
NODE1_URL="http://<IP_SERVER_B>:8081/engine-rest/engine"
NODE2_URL="http://<IP_SERVER_B>:8082/engine-rest/engine"

check_url() {
    local name=$1
    local url=$2
    if curl -sf --max-time 5 "$url" | grep -q "default"; then
        echo "[OK] $name"
    else
        echo "[FAIL] $name - $url"
    fi
}

echo "=== Camunda Health Check: $(date) ==="
check_url "Nginx LB" "$NGINX_URL"
check_url "Camunda1" "$NODE1_URL"
check_url "Camunda2" "$NODE2_URL"
echo ""
```

```bash
sudo chmod +x /opt/camunda-healthcheck.sh

# Chạy thủ công
/opt/camunda-healthcheck.sh

# Hoặc cron mỗi 5 phút
sudo crontab -e
# Thêm dòng:
# */5 * * * * /opt/camunda-healthcheck.sh >> /var/log/camunda-health.log 2>&1
